### Place an order
POST http://localhost:5000/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerEmail": "dev@example.com",
  "lines": [
    { "sku": "SKU-001", "quantity": 2, "unitPrice": 9.99 },
    { "sku": "SKU-002", "quantity": 1, "unitPrice": 19.50 }
  ]
}

### Get order by id (replace the id)
GET http://localhost:5000/v1/orders/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
